&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Image:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/social-media"&gt;OONI Explorer thematic censorship pages&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today we are excited to announce the publication of new &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/"&gt;OONI Explorer&lt;/a&gt; thematic censorship pages! These new pages include charts and reports documenting the blocking of &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/social-media"&gt;social media&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/news-media"&gt;news media&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/circumvention"&gt;circumvention tools&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; around the world based on OONI data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this blog post, we share information about the new OONI Explorer thematic censorship pages.&lt;/p&gt;
